Alert

It is a small box with information and required action

Simple alert/Confirmation alert
contains a small information along with the action like ok or cancel

prompt alert
required inpout from the user

How to handle the alert

driver.switchTo.alert.dismiss= cancel
driver.switchTo.alert.accept= ok
driver.swithcTo.alert.getText()= to capture the alert message
or use alert class
Alert alert=driver.switchTo.alert
